## âš¡ï¸ Key Features

- ðŸ’¬ Natural language chat API with async support  
- ðŸ§  Define unique AI personas with custom system prompts  
- ðŸŽ¯ Fine-grained control over temperature, token limits, and creativity  
- ðŸ§µ Persistent conversation state (threaded dialog)  
- ðŸ”„ Supports parallel conversations with isolated agents  
- ðŸ§© Minimal setup with powerful config-based architecture  

